### Welcome to the GitHub page of Frogurth.
I'm currently working on the ["CSN"](https://github.com/GeeksOfTheDusk/CSN)-project as a member of @GeeksOfTheDusk.

### My projects on GitHub
 * [CSVReader](https://github.com/Frogurth/CSVReader) - Scala library to parse a csv-formatted file.
 * [shiny-bear](https://github.com/Frogurth/shiny-bear) - Very basic haskell CSV parser.
 * [QuickNoting](https://github.com/Frogurth/QuickNoting) - Commandline tool written in scala to quickly make notes.
 * [RCAP](https://github.com/Frogurth/RCAP) - Application to broadcast the content of the system clipboard in a private LAN.
